OL,3,CUK minister praises Jersey's bus
OL,4,Cservice as the 'gold standard'
OL,6,FJersey's bus service is the "gold
OL,7,Fstandard" for transport links in
OL,8,Fsmaller towns and rural areas,
OL,9,Faccording to a UK Government minister.
OL,11,FSimon Lightwood is the British Local
OL,12,FTransport Minister and says Jersey is
OL,13,Fa "remarkable success story" that is
OL,14,Fnow being put forward by the UK
OL,15,FGovernment as a shining example in its
OL,16,Fbid to give local authorities there
OL,17,Fmore control over how buses are run.
