OL,3,CUK minister praises Jersey's bus
OL,4,Cservice as the 'gold standard'
OL,6,FMr Lightwood says his Government will
OL,7,Fbring the Bus Services Bill to the
OL,8,FHouse of Commons "very soon" for
OL,9,Fdebate.
OL,11,FThe Minister adds he was impressed by
OL,12,Fa 47% increase in bus passengers
OL,13,Facross Jersey since LibertyBus took
OL,14,Fover the service in 2013.
OL,16,FThat upward trend defies the dropping
OL,17,Fcoverage of buses in the UK, where bus
OL,18,Fmileage fell by a quarter between 2005
OL,19,Fand 2024 outside London.
