OL,3,CUK minister praises Jersey's bus
OL,4,Cservice as the 'gold standard'
OL,6,FMr Lightwood explains: "I very much
OL,7,Fsee Jersey as the gold standard of
OL,8,Ffranchising when it comes to more
OL,9,Frural and smaller towns, the same way
OL,10,Fas I see Manchester as the gold
OL,11,Fstandard for urban areas, so very much
OL,12,Fa beacon."
OL,14,FSpeaking about what lessons can be
OL,15,Ftaken away from his trip to Jersey,
OL,16,Fthe Minister adds: "I've learnt how
OL,17,Fimportant it is that bus companies are
OL,18,Fembedded in the community, that they
OL,19,Ftruly reflect the needs of the
OL,20,Fcommunity in which they serve.
