OL,3,CUK minister praises Jersey's bus
OL,4,Cservice as the 'gold standard'
OL,6,F"That's why it's so important we (the
OL,7,FUK Government) take back control, that
OL,8,Flocal communities are able to shape
OL,9,Fthose bus services that truly get them
OL,10,Fto where they want to be."
OL,12,FMr Lightwood also praised the way
OL,13,Flocal leaders in Jersey have been able
OL,14,Fto shape the way the service is
OL,15,Foperated.
OL,17,FMr Lightwood says: "We've got a long
OL,18,Fway to go in many areas of the UK to
OL,19,Fachieve what has been a fantastic
OL,20,Fresult here in Jersey.
