OL,3,CUK minister praises Jersey's bus
OL,4,Cservice as the 'gold standard'
OL,6,F"That 47% increase in passengers
OL,7,Fnumbers is remarkable, especially
OL,8,Fgiven the Covid pandemic.
OL,10,F"We always want to continue to
OL,11,Fimprove, always listening, and that's
OL,12,Fwhat it's all about. Listening to
OL,13,Flocal communities to offer the
OL,14,Fservices they deserve."
OL,16,FSince taking over from MyBus 12 years
OL,17,Fago, LibertyBus introduced a flat rate
OL,18,Fof #2 for all single journeys around
OL,19,Fthe island in 2016, a sum which has
OL,20,Fgradually risen.
