OL,6,FIt currently costs #2.55 for an adult
OL,7,Fsingle ticket if paying by contactless
OL,8,Fcard, or #3 by cash.
OL,10,FSome authorities in the UK operate a
OL,11,Fsimilar model with single bus fares in
OL,12,FLondon, Greater Manchester, West
OL,13,FYorkshire, Northumberland, Tyne and
OL,14,FWear and County Durham all currently
OL,15,Fcapped.
